      "role": "user",
      "content": "okay that makes more sense thanks. so if the liver is converting it back to glucose, does that mean i'm basically recycling stuff while i'm working out? and does the burning actually come from the lactate itself or is it something else happening in the muscle cells?",
      "source": "evaluator"
